## Layout

- `docs/` — human-written source of truth: plan, specs, [ADR-Lean](docs/ADR-Lean.md), runbooks.
- `raw/` — read-only mirror of `docs/` for AI ingest. **Never edit by hand.**
- `wiki/` — AI-managed knowledge base. Query starts at [wiki/index.md](wiki/index.md). See [WIKI.md](WIKI.md).
- `src/{{SERVICE_SLUG}}/` — application code.
- `tests/` — unit + integration tests (≥80% coverage on new code).
- `scripts/` — operational scripts (incl. `sync_raw_mirror.sh` for the docs→raw hook).
